# Pin npm resolution to the PUBLIC npm registry.
#
# Why: since GitHub's 2026-06-23 "Automatic Dependabot access to GitHub-hosted registries" rollout,
# Dependabot probes https://npm.pkg.github.com/ for every package. Most public packages 404 there and
# fall back to npmjs, but @types/node returns a STALE 200 (capped at 17.0.18), so pnpm resolution of our
# @types/node@^24 devDep fails (ERR_PNPM_NO_MATCHING_VERSION) on every npm Dependabot run. Pinning the
# default registry and the @types scope to npmjs tells pnpm to resolve them from the real registry.
#
# No-op for local dev / CI / publish (npmjs is already pnpm's default); this just makes it explicit so
# Dependabot's injected GitHub Packages routing can't shadow it.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
@types:registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
